{"tid":616241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高鐵出軌】港鐵員工短訊流傳出事前維修中心閘門「無故震動 」","createTime":"2018-04-04T04:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T09:03:51.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"736307524ace501e18a15a1d0a00c3482c1e992a","tid":616241,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180404/large/1522813827_e80a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180404%2Flarge%2F1522813827_e80a.png&h=4ec536c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正進行試行的廣深港高速鐵路（香港段），周二晚（3日）發生罕見列車出軌意外，事件迅速在港鐵員工的Whatsapp群組內流傳，港鐵則在凌晨2時向傳媒發稿證實事件。<br />\n<br />\n根據員工群組流傳的版本，涉事列車（編號EMU0256）昨夜7時許返回石崗列車停放處，並以慢速進入有蓋維修中心，職員在閉路電視發現中心閘門無故出現震動，列車司機一度停車並下車查看，不過未有發現，於是繼續開車慢駛，列車隨即出軌。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵其後在凌晨2時發稿公佈涉事出軌意外，指昨晚約9時15分，車廠工程人員進行巡查時發現一列停泊於維修車庫的高鐵列車，其尾卡部份車輪偏離路軌，事件中無人受傷；該列列車在昨日較早時進行試運行後，返回石崗列車停放。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，非常關注有關情況，將就事件進行詳細調查，並已通知機電工程署。"},{"pid":"feecc010264add1170afd989d5bb64bf78e312ea","tid":616241,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09c038ce4069f5b153c4df0c721fe407de6417c2","tid":616241,"uid":99205,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:45:35.000Z","msg":"無事自主撚發<br />\n有事外國技術<br />\n<br />\n支那制造不意外"},{"pid":"cf28fab7c641a93d8cf9c0786b65314aec37363b","tid":616241,"uid":14918,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:46:18.000Z","msg":"何以感震動？"},{"pid":"6460b1e9d178fbd34a1eaf49c331d7d9926c974f","tid":616241,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:47:05.000Z","msg":"車震？"},{"pid":"556330396252ad461b3c622271b196b06b0aabda","tid":616241,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:47:35.000Z","msg":"動感"},{"pid":"8acc67d39f475938e842f187def296281f0da756","tid":616241,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:47:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffce3c83ff53bbde5ab541932f472b728d5e5e1d","tid":616241,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3adf50b39ca7235724a928003cab263e49c3f55c","tid":616241,"uid":63017,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"feecc010264add1170afd989d5bb64bf78e312ea","tid":616241,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"記者問題"},{"pid":"4f5f5b9e393b20d15653553c536e653a310bd5d1","tid":616241,"uid":36901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T05:45:10.000Z","msg":"cls,慢速都出軌<br />\n對上港鐵出軌係幾年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3b226982906486810d023c7c193864f8be311d","tid":616241,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}